                </li>
                <li class="com-item">
                    <img src="/images/siteType/xiangy/items-advantage-2.png" alt="">
                    <p>交互流畅、体验更好</p>
                </li>
                <li class="com-item">
                    <img src="/images/siteType/xiangy/items-advantage-3.png" alt="">
                    <p>布局合理、形象统一</p>
